        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Those cunning bastards.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 106,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 107,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Asimov falls silent when you\\'re done telling him about what Echo has been up to. A moment later, he speaks again.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 108,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'I\\'ll try my best to keep Babylonia out of this, but you\\'ll have to get your hands on the data at Utopia before Babylonia finds out what you\\'ve been up to.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 109,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'I\\'ll do everything I can.', 3: '110', 4: 'Shouldn\\'t be a problem.', 5: '110'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 110,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'I just processed the data you sent my way and forwarded it to Nikola and Wells.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 111,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'We have no idea where that Construct came from, so the data is meant for them to use as a bargaining chip if Kurono ever finds out about this.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 112,
        "ActionId": 112,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Right, but Wells?', 3: '113'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 113,
        "ActionId": 113,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Yup. As far as this goes, Wells has been treading very lightly. An insider told me that Wells had once led an excellent squad that they called Silver Falcon.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 114,
        "ActionId": 114,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Except they got wiped out completely doing a simple surface mission, and the mission location was Conservation Area 112.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 115,
        "ActionId": 115,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Conservation Area 112...', 3: '116'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 116,
        "ActionId": 116,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You remember seeing Conservation Area 112... in a report of Fort Winter—\"A conservation area destroyed by Hetero-Creatures\" is how it was described.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 117,
        "ActionId": 117,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'I bet Kurono was behind that.', 3: '118'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 118,
        "ActionId": 118,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'We have nothing definite to back that up, but...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 119,
        "ActionId": 119,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Asimov nods at you.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 120,
        "ActionId": 120,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: '...By the way, I sent her data report to the Control Court a week ago.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 121,
        "ActionId": 121,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Asimov nods at you. There are always certain things that shouldn\\'t be talked about even over an encrypted channel.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 122,
        "ActionId": 122,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'I\\'ll send her down to Earth to \"look into abnormal samples\" as soon as I have a chance.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 123,
        "ActionId": 123,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 124,
        "ActionId": 124,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You know exactly who Asimov is referring to.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 125,
        "ActionId": 125,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'That sounds great!', 3: '126'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 126,
        "ActionId": 126,
